fetchCurrencies.description: Fetches all available currencies on an exchange

fetchMarkets.description: Retrieves data on all markets for cube

fetchOHLCV.description: Fetches historical candlestick data containing the open, high, low, and close price, and the volume of a market

fetchOrderBook.description: Fetches information on open orders with bid (buy) and ask (sell) prices, volumes and other data

fetchStatus.description: The latest known information on the availability of the exchange API

fetchTicker.description: Fetches a price ticker, a statistical calculation with the information calculated over the past 24 hours for a specific market

fetchTrades.description: Get the list of most recent trades for a particular symbol
